    "content": "<h2>Teplota</h2>\n<p><strong>Teplota</strong> je fyzikální veličina vyjadřující míru „zahřátosti\" tělesa. Značíme ji <strong>t</strong> (ve °C) nebo <strong>T</strong> (v kelvinech).</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:center;margin:1.5rem auto;max-width:520px;\"><svg viewBox='0 0 400 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' style='width:100%;font-family:sans-serif'>\n  <text x='100' y='18' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='13'>Teploměr</text>\n  <rect x='90' y='25' width='20' height='140' rx='10' fill='#f3f4f6' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <circle cx='100' cy='170' r='14' fill='#ef4444' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <rect x='95' y='80' width='10' height='85' rx='5' fill='#ef4444'/>\n  <line x1='110' y1='30' x2='120' y2='30' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='125' y='34' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>100°C — var</text><line x1='110' y1='60' x2='120' y2='60' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='125' y='64' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>50°C</text><line x1='110' y1='90' x2='120' y2='90' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='125' y='94' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>0°C — tání</text><line x1='110' y1='120' x2='120' y2='120' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='125' y='124' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>-20°C</text><line x1='110' y1='150' x2='120' y2='150' stroke='#374151' stroke-width='1'/><text x='125' y='154' fill='#374151' font-size='10'>-40°C</text>\n  <line x1='115' y1='80' x2='125' y2='80' stroke='#ef4444' stroke-width='2'/>\n  <text x='127' y='84' fill='#ef4444' font-size='10' font-weight='bold'>← 37°C</text>\n  <rect x='260' y='40' width='120' height='130' rx='8' fill='#eff6ff' stroke='#3b82f6' stroke-width='1.5'/>\n  <text x='320' y='65' text-anchor='middle' font-weight='bold' fill='#1e40af' font-size='12'>Převod</text>\n  <text x='320' y='90' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>T = t + 273</text>\n  <text x='320' y='115' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>0 °C = 273 K</text>\n  <text x='320' y='140' text-anchor='middle' fill='#374151' font-size='12'>100 °C = 373 K</text>\n  <text x='320' y='165' text-anchor='middle' fill='#ef4444' font-size='11'>−273 °C = 0 K</text>\n</svg></div><h3>Teplotní stupnice</h3>\n<table><thead><tr><th>Stupnice</th><th>Jednotka</th><th>Bod mrazu vody</th><th>Bod varu vody</th></tr></thead><tbody>\n<tr><td>Celsiova</td><td>°C</td><td>0 °C</td><td>100 °C</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Kelvinova</td><td>K</td><td>273 K</td><td>373 K</td></tr>\n<tr><td>Fahrenheitova</td><td>°F</td><td>32 °F</td><td>212 °F</td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n<h3>Převod Celsia ↔ Kelvin</h3>\n<div class='formula'>$$T = t + 273$$</div>\n<div class='formula'>$$t = T - 273$$</div>\n<h3>Měření teploty</h3>\n<p><strong>Teploměr</strong> — kapalinový (rtuťový, lihový), digitální, bimetalový.</p>\n<p>Princip: látka se při zahřátí <strong>roztahuje</strong> (teplotní roztažnost).</p>\n<p><strong>Absolutní nula</strong> = 0 K = −273,15 °C (nejnižší možná teplota, částice se přestanou pohybovat).</p>"
  }
}
